{"tid":2411483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"眾新聞 河北南宮市逾40日未解封  惹居民不滿：捱貴菜 食老本 敢怒不敢言","createTime":"2021-02-17T10:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T01:51:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc85cc02476ed97b1530709c994c854980e6225","tid":2411483,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"眾新聞<br />\n河北南宮市逾40日未解封 <br />\n惹居民不滿：捱貴菜 食老本 敢怒不敢言<br />\nFeb 17, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mR-vTH79VUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmR-vTH79VUA&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2z11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=e851c5e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mR-vTH79VUA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n57.8K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n【敢怒不敢言】河北南宮市1月初新增確診病例後，當地政府下令在全市實施家居隔離，至今超過40日未解封，約36萬名居民的新年都在隔離中度過。<br />\n<br />\n大批居民在微博質疑，為何南宮市已降至低風險地區，但仍然未解封。有居民指做了26次核酸檢測都是陰性，亦有孕婦指產前檢查都做不了。網上流傳市內仍有確診病例，但官方沒公佈，因而不能解封。<br />\n<br />\n令居民困擾的還包括物資供應問題，有當地人向我們表示，要靠自己上網搶官方指定的高價菜，目前只是靠積蓄過活，敢怒不敢言。"},{"pid":"433bce8c3f8a2f0571488723da0cf0ce79efc602","tid":2411483,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:01:18.000Z","msg":"假封城,真回血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce2e14e0714ff0dc85f244feb49ca86e9f4ac9f","tid":2411483,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a46d7569e8284d4dc3fe360ab74c79c06797180","tid":2411483,"uid":67771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"敢怒不敢言就自己收皮啦"},{"pid":"3c4d81e3f9528a47bf62e921bc3c300dd83fc2c4","tid":2411483,"uid":79563,"like":0,"di